ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectRemission Order in Respect of Certain Fees for the Issuance of Identity and Travel Documents (Port of Beirut Explosions)
PrecisREMISSION ORDER IN RESPECT OF CERTAIN FEES FOR THE ISSUANCE OF IDENTITY AND TRAVEL DOCUMENTS (PORT OF BEIRUT EXPLOSIONS) in order to remit the fees for the issuance of travel documents and certificates of Canadian citizenship for those impacted by the August 2020 Port of Beirut explosions.
